replies.body:
Most champions at release are extremely over powered and need nerfs. Just to name a few: {{champion:122}} {{champion:60}} {{champion:121}} {{champion:236}} {{champion:111}} {{champion:107}} {{champion:238}} 
This doesn't disqualify being upset about the newest champion, but it puts it into perspective. Another thing to note is several OLDER champions became over powered as the meta changed, for example {{champion:68}} {{champion:92}} {{champion:102}} {{champion:80}} {{champion:84}} {{champion:103}} {{champion:26}} 
I honestly think we need more bans per team.
